partnerDetails.about:
With 10 years of expertise in the marketplace, CT knows there is always a better way to deliver more resilient,
& customer-focused Data Centres. Through collaboration & inspired designs, we constantly challenge
Data Centre construction and operation. We adhere to utilize cutting-edge technologies as well as
our in-house experts to analyze requirements, drivers and constraints and ultimately provide the best
designed Data Centre facility.
